'''斯洛文尼亚共和国国民议会'''（Državni zbor Republike Slovenije）是[[斯洛文尼亚|斯洛文尼亚]]的立法机关。根据宪法，国民议会是[[兩院制|兩院制]]中的下议院和最主要的组成部分，议会中的最大党或党派联盟有组建内阁的权力<ref name="US2008">{{cite article |url=http://odlocitve.us-rs.si/usrs/us-odl.nsf/o/91B69BBC50349012C12574F2004123EB |title=U-I-295/07-8 |date=22 October 2008 |accessdate=16 December 2010 |language=sl |publisher=Constitutional Court of the Republic of Slovenia |archive-date=2011-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110823141430/http://odlocitve.us-rs.si/usrs/us-odl.nsf/o/91B69BBC50349012C12574F2004123EB |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |url=http://dk.fdv.uni-lj.si/dela/Lakota-Igor.PDF |title=Sistem nepopolne dvodomnosti v slovenskem parlamentu (diplomska naloga) |trans_title=The system of incomplete bicameralism in the Slovenian Parliament (diploma thesis} |page=62 |first=Igor |last=Lakota |year=2006 |accessdate=16 December 2010 |publisher=Faculty of Social Sciences, University of Ljubljana |language=sl |quote=Opinions differ, however the majority of domestic experts agree that the National Council may be regarded as the upper house, but the bicameralism is distinctively incomplete.}}</ref>。总共有90个议席，每四年选举一次，其中88席由各政党派出代表参选，其余2席由少数族裔即讲[[意大利语|意大利语]]和[[匈牙利语|匈牙利语]]的斯洛维尼亚人按照[[波達計數法|波達計數法]]各自选举产生，选举出来的这两个议员必须维护本族裔的利益。

